title: Frank Kaminsky Busts Out Some Crazy Dance Moves for Fans in China
text:
Frank Kaminsky isn't afraid to be seen getting his dance on.
He was featured in a brief spot that ran on CBS during the NCAA tournament where he did his best Carlton dance , and has appeared on film busting some goofy moves on at least a couple of other occasions .
So it's not surprising, then, that when the Charlotte Hornets were in China for a recent preseason contest, Kaminsky was the one picked to go to center court to make sure the fans got their money's worth.
